data.text:
For the promo to their rousing single Counting Stars, James Lees films a spirited performance by OneRepublic who've set up shop in a dusty, damp warehouse space (complete with a roaming aligator).

The action is complimented with a sidebar narrative of a preacher and his followers getting a bit over enthusiastic, it has to be said...
